WEBVTT

00:01.870 --> 00:03.625
<i>Previously on "Zero Hour"...</i>

00:06.506 --> 00:08.138
They're breaking in!

00:08.173 --> 00:10.341
We know quite a bit about
who might have her...

00:10.376 --> 00:12.210
The highest-end mercenary
in the world.

00:12.244 --> 00:13.378
It's about a clock.

00:13.413 --> 00:16.146
1938, the church appoints
12 new apostles

00:16.181 --> 00:18.716
and trusts them with
the ultimate secret,

00:18.750 --> 00:20.017
and it's hidden in these clocks.

00:20.051 --> 00:22.753
I solve this, I find Laila.

00:22.788 --> 00:25.188
(Arron) The guy in the sub,
he looked like you?

00:25.223 --> 00:28.191
He looked <i>exactly</i> like me.

00:28.226 --> 00:30.294
How did you end up
working for the FBI?

00:30.328 --> 00:31.629
Plane blows up on
the other side of the planet.

00:31.663 --> 00:33.263
You're husband's on it,

00:33.298 --> 00:34.997
and suddenly you just wanna put
a bullet in the bomber's head.

00:35.032 --> 00:36.999
Laila!
Hank!

00:37.034 --> 00:38.200
I'll find you!

00:41.305 --> 00:45.408
<i>(Ticking)</i>

00:45.528 --> 00:48.926
<font color=#00FFFF>Zero Hour 01x03</font>
<font color="#ffff00">Pendulum</font>
Original Air Date February 28, 2013

00:49.046 --> 00:51.313
<i>(White Vincent)</i>
<i>2 is the number of love,</i>

00:51.347 --> 00:54.850
<i>life's everlasting breath.</i>

00:54.884 --> 00:59.955
<i>Sometimes its blind pursuit</i>
<i>leads not to life</i>

00:59.989 --> 01:01.824
<i>but death.</i>

01:02.482 --> 01:05.926
